(260, 1, '2016-07-24 19:31:05', '2016-07-24 19:31:05', '\r\nSolution :\r\nStep1:  Goto C:\\xampp\\apache\\conf\\extra\\httpd-vhosts.conf or find  httpd-vhosts.conf file in your apache\r\nStep2: Add following line in your vhosts.conf file \r\n<blockquote>\r\n\r\n    ServerName localhost.laravel.dev\r\n    DocumentRoot "C:/xampp/htdocs/www/laravel5/public"\r\n    SetEnv APPLICATION_ENV "development"\r\n    \r\n        DirectoryIndex index.php\r\n        AllowOverride All\r\n        Order allow,deny\r\n        Allow from all\r\n    \r\n\r\nStep3 : Restart your server.\r\n\r\nThanks :)', 'How to create vhost in window xampp?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'how-to-create-vhost-in-window-xampp', '', '', '2016-07-25 03:09:54', '2016-07-25 03:09:54', '', 0, 'http://programmerlab.com/dwqa-question/how-to-create-vhost-in-window-xampp/', 0, 'dwqa-question', '', 0),
