(262, 0, '2016-07-24 19:41:32', '2016-07-24 19:41:32', 'Step1: Goto C:\\xampp\\apache\\conf\\extra\\httpd-vhosts.conf or find httpd-vhosts.conf file in your apache<br />Step2: Add following line in your vhosts.conf file\r\n<blockquote>\r\nServerName localhost.laravel.dev<br />DocumentRoot C:/xampp/htdocs/www/laravel5/public<br />SetEnv APPLICATION_ENV development\r\nDirectoryIndex index.php<br />AllowOverride All<br />Order allow,deny<br />Allow from all\r\nstep3:<span>and edit the file System32/Drivers/etc/hosts use notepad as administrator</span>\r\nStep3 : Restart your server.\r\n</blockquote>\r\nadd bottom of the file\r\n<pre><code><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: #7d2727">127.0</span><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: #303336">.</span><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: #7d2727">0.1</span><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: #303336">    www</span><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: #303336">.</span><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: #303336">siteurl</span><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: #303336">.</span><span style="margin: 0px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: #303336">com</span></code></pre>', 'Answer for How to create vhost in window xampp?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-how-to-create-vhost-in-window-xampp', '', '', '2016-07-24 19:41:32', '2016-07-24 19:41:32', '', 260, 'http://programmerlab.com/dwqa-answer/answer-for-how-to-create-vhost-in-window-xampp/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 1),
